column5: Jeez, it took me a coupla years or so but I have over 1,000 posts!! Let's see how long it takes me to get to 2,000.
lol nice.. i think i might catch up pretty soon LOL!
congrats! maybe its time to walk away from the computer, stretch, maybe take a shower, have a shave. Grab a snack before you get back at it....

Oh yeah, and I'm a Fishing Icon now!!LOL
Well then, Congratulations and champagne all around!!
